Each player is given 3 refunds to use for situations such as this. If you've already use them or you purchased it in a bundle or mystery gift, then unfortunately you may be out of luck. Information on Refund tokens can be found here;

https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201751864-Content-Refund-FAQ

If you're unable to refund it, you can still try asking Player Support in a [Support Ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).
